name: Bee Play #6
description:
"Bee Play", a limited series centered around images of bees, and
executed using a variety of methods.

In the exif data of each image, you can see the precise mix of seed
information used to generate the image using a conversational GAN
network in combination with seed images and sketches.  I typically
generate thousands of attempts with many different seed texts, after
which I manually work with the best of them to complete the artistic
vision.

Thank you for taking the time to enjoy my art.  It's delightfully fun
and rewarding both to make and to get better at making, I hope you
like it too.

This series is my first on Tezos, and consists of a limited run of 16
artworks, released starting October 15, 2021.
